title: Is This Ghislaine Maxwell’s Unsealed ‘List of Names’?
subtitle: The list of dozens of names posted to Facebook was offered up in connection with the Jeffrey Epstein sex-trafficking case.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A list of public figures posted to Facebook was part of an "unsealed" list of names kept by Ghislaine Maxwell, who has been charged with facilitating the sexual abuse of minors by Jeffrey Epstein.
